[4] Nepal
Date: Sat, 10 Sep 2005
From: ProMED-mail <promed@promedmail.org>
Source: XinHuaNet.com [edited]
<http://english.people.com.cn/200509/10/eng20050910_207742.html>

At least 15 typhoid patients are reportedly arriving each day at Lami
primary Health Center of Dang district, Nepal.
